Experienced in Beauty industry would be advantaged
Minimum 2 years relevant work experience in publishing, editing or copy writing;
Experience in creative writing, blogging or publications is highly preferable;
Excellent in Chinese and English written skill;
To be responsible, organized, proactive and self-motivated

